Description:
circa late 60s/early 70s Crestwood electric guitar, made in Japan, in a really cool cherry finish in excellent condition.  Any fan of older vintage Japanese electrics will love this little Crestwood.  Really nice cherry finish, cool mirror pickguard - nice sounding pickups.  Looks to be all original - an excellent addition to any MIJ collection!
